    <Text text="Patch Notes" fontSize="34" color="#F3F6FA" fontStyle="Bold" offsetXY="0 220" alignment="MiddleCenter"/>
    <Text text="* Dropped support for 10E legacy&#10;* Gaining or Decreasing CP via widget or overlay now is logged in chat for tracking.&#10;* Added colours to disposition picker for better matching&#10;* Added deployment picker based on disposition, currently we only have 3 deployment zones per disposition match up but that will change as GW shows more stuff.&#10;* Added VP limitations for primary, secondaries and total scores.&#10;* Changed scoreboard buttons&#10;* Added the option to change table mat (more to come!)&#10;* Lots of new tokens!&#10;* Major code cleanup." fontSize="26" color="#D8E1EA" offsetXY="0 -40" width="1280" height="400" alignment="UpperLeft"/>
  </Panel>

